<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ briefing.title }} — 팩트렌즈</title>
    <meta name="description" content="AI가 뉴스를 쉽게 요약하고 팩트체크 검증 태그를 붙여주는 중립적 뉴스 브리핑">
    <meta name="google-site-verification" content="VnZBNB4MhsZ77uMB9_2FT-9FhTBkYhJYy6OGxh4GFxU">
    <meta name="naver-site-verification" content="e956417c1cf0f10b3cd7af7198c2ce6370bccb77">
    <meta property="og:title" content="{{ briefing.title }} — 팩트렌즈">
    <meta property="og:description" content="팩트가 검증된 쉬운 뉴스 브리핑 — 진실을 보는 렌즈">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://factlens.pages.dev/">
    <meta property="og:locale" content="ko_KR">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="{{ briefing.title }} — 팩트렌즈">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="팩트가 검증된 쉬운 뉴스 브리핑 — 진실을 보는 렌즈">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/style.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="/static/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
    <script async src="https://t1.daumcdn.net/kas/static/ba.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Google Analytics (GA4) -->
    <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-RYQSQF9486"></script>
    <script>window.dataLayer=window.dataLayer||[];function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}gtag('js',new Date());gtag('config','G-RYQSQF9486');</script>
    <!-- Microsoft Clarity -->
    <script>(function(c,l,a,r,i,t,y){c[a]=c[a]||function(){(c[a].q=c[a].q||[]).push(arguments)};t=l.createElement(r);t.async=1;t.src="https://www.clarity.ms/tag/"+i;y=l.getElementsByTagName(r)[0];y.parentNode.insertBefore(t,y)})(window,document,"clarity","script","vp0n1nogns");</script>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="site-header">
        <h1 class="site-title">팩트렌즈</h1>
        <p class="tagline">팩트가 검증된 쉬운 뉴스 브리핑</p>
    </header>

    <main class="briefing">
        <h2 class="briefing-title">{{ briefing.title }}</h2>

        {% for article in briefing.articles %}
        <article class="news-card">
            <h3 class="card-headline">{{ article.headline }}</h3>

            <section class="card-summary">
                {% for paragraph in article.summary.split('\n\n') %}
                <p>{{ paragraph }}</p>
                {% endfor %}
            </section>

            <section class="card-verification">
                {% if article.verification_tag == 'verified' %}
                <span class="tag tag--verified">&#x2705; 사실 확인됨</span>
                {% elif article.verification_tag == 'unconfirmed' %}
                <span class="tag tag--unconfirmed">&#x26A0;&#xFE0F; 사실 확인 중</span>
                {% elif article.verification_tag == 'misleading' %}
                <span class="tag tag--misleading">&#x274C; 왜곡/오류</span>
                {% endif %}
                <p class="verification-reason">{{ article.verification_reason }}</p>
                {% if article.verification_tag != 'unconfirmed' and article.evidence_links %}
                <details class="evidence-toggle">
                    <summary>출처 확인하기 ({{ article.evidence_links | length }}건)</summary>
                    <ul class="evidence-list">
                        {% for evidence in article.evidence_links %}
                        <li><a href="{{ evidence.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ evidence.title }}</a></li>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </ul>
                    {% if article.search_entry_point %}
                    <div class="search-widget">
                        {{ article.search_entry_point | safe }}
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}
                </details>
                {% endif %}
            </section>

            <section class="card-sources">
                <h4>원문 보기</h4>
                <ul class="source-list">
                    {% for source in article.source_articles %}
                    <li><a href="{{ source.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ source.publisher }}</a></li>
                    {% endfor %}
                    {% if article.original_url %}
                    <li><a href="{{ article.original_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ article.publisher if article.publisher else '원문' }}</a></li>
                    {% endif %}
                </ul>
            </section>
        </article>
        {% if loop.index == 3 %}
        <div class="mid-support-banner">
            <a class="support-link" href="https://buymeacoffee.com/handaram" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                가짜뉴스 없는 세상, 후원으로 함께 만들어주세요
            </a>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if loop.index == 7 %}
        <div class="ad-banner">
            <ins class="kakao_ad_area" style="display:none;"
                 data-ad-unit="DAN-H8O06nayAbOwWLLC"
                 data-ad-width="320"
                 data-ad-height="100"></ins>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer">
        <p class="disclaimer">AI 기반 자동 검증이며, 최종 판단은 독자의 몫입니다.</p>
        <a class="support-link" href="https://buymeacoffee.com/handaram" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            가짜뉴스 없는 세상, 후원으로 함께 만들어주세요
        </a>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
